<p class="">It is material that the House should know whether this new arrangement, whereby the First Lord of the Admiralty had certain new powers of direction over the Committee of the Chiefs of Staff, covered the period of the Norwegian operations, or is it since the Norwegian operations commenced?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
