<p class="">I said that they would take a heavy toll.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-02a56a8e-dd93-443f-ad1e-7cba233ea2db" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
