                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Ships were ready, but they were not troopships.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ed6733b8-f077-4872-b933-b19f9045772c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-07/debates/ee7fb681-43ae-4a17-a06f-cdf0a62e1ce2/ConductOfTheWar#contribution-ed6733b8-f077-4872-b933-b19f9045772c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-c3cedaed-9ce6-41f4-a286-9b475f0cbfb2">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-c3cedaed-9ce6-41f4-a286-9b475f0cbfb2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-c3cedaed-9ce6-41f4-a286-9b475f0cbfb2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c3cedaed-9ce6-41f4-a286-9b475f0cbfb2">
                Sir A. Sinclair
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c3cedaed-9ce6-41f4-a286-9b475f0cbfb2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-07/debates/ee7fb681-43ae-4a17-a06f-cdf0a62e1ce2/ConductOfTheWar#contribution-c3cedaed-9ce6-41f4-a286-9b475f0cbfb2">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">They did not use troopships? They were all transported in warships?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c3cedaed-9ce6-41f4-a286-9b475f0cbfb2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-07/debates/ee7fb681-43ae-4a17-a06f-cdf0a62e1ce2/ConductOfTheWar#contribution-c3cedaed-9ce6-41f4-a286-9b475f0cbfb2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
