            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-953e62c8-b3e8-4069-8eef-db59b8921d10">
                The Secretary of State for War (Mr. Oliver Stanley)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-953e62c8-b3e8-4069-8eef-db59b8921d10" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
