<p class="">As yours did at Munich.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-97473e09-97cc-4813-a1cf-b57b82a8c9dc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
