        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-433b424d-b395-42c1-ac63-c7081484ec25">
                Mr. Stanley
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-433b424d-b395-42c1-ac63-c7081484ec25" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-07/debates/ee7fb681-43ae-4a17-a06f-cdf0a62e1ce2/ConductOfTheWar#contribution-433b424d-b395-42c1-ac63-c7081484ec25">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">After all, it has been the War Office which has been issuing the communiqués of the progress on land.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-433b424d-b395-42c1-ac63-c7081484ec25" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-05-07/debates/ee7fb681-43ae-4a17-a06f-cdf0a62e1ce2/ConductOfTheWar#contribution-433b424d-b395-42c1-ac63-c7081484ec25">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
