<p class="">I do not know whether the Noble Lady has read a remarkable book by an hon. and gallant Member of this House, the hon. and gallant Member for Carlisle (Brigadier-General Spears), entitled "Prelude to Victory" If not, let her read it—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
